{"tid":1132897,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"三年A班","createTime":"2019-04-30T15:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T17:09:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"34bd5ea9f30202a1cb0a507565602088ec47726b","tid":1132897,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190426/20664108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664108&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1VR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=595df5fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664108&h=5cc8f11b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190426/20664108</a><br />\n<br />\n三年A班 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190426/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190426%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=2e3ea54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《3年A班》劇照<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不能不佩服日本人的創意，以及揭露社會問題時毫不手軟的冷洌。最近在看的一套日劇是《三年A班》，校園故事，題材卻相當沉重。<br />\n<br />\n面對教而不善、教而不化的學生，宅男似備受學生欺凌的老師，在學生畢業離校前十天，決定給他們上人生最後一課。先是宣佈「此刻開始，你們都是我的人質。」然後用炸彈炸毀教學樓，把29個學生圍困住。<br />\n<br />\n平素低眉順眼、看起來手無縛雞之力的文弱書生，原來一身好功夫，小時候的志願竟然是動作片演員。既然不能教化學生，索性用武力解決，甚至不惜殺了他們。<br />\n<br />\n只看了前面幾集，劇情不難想像，29個學生想必會展開殘酷的困獸鬥，電視要揭露的，似乎不只是社會問題，更是人性之陰暗。飾演男主角的是被日本網民視作「花樣美男」的菅田將暉。他瘦削單薄的身形、文弱而陰鬱的氣質、憂鬱的眼神與角色非常吻合。<br />\n<br />\n每個學生都有鮮明的個性，劇本在刻畫人物性格方面頗下苦功。飾演班長的永野芽郁在繼《帝一之國》後，與菅田將暉再度合作，永野把掩藏自己真實想法，小心揣摩他人看法以迎合大眾，在社會努力求存的小人物角色演繹得相當出色。<br />\n<br />\n劇中一個早已經不存在，卻又無處不在的角色，是課室內第30名學生，如幽靈般穿梭其間。是貫穿劇本的經絡。<br />\n<br />\n把校園想像成社會，每個人不妨想想自己扮演的是哪一個角色。想必深受觸動。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n掌聲喝采只是假象 (蔣芸)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n送別陶然 (林道群)"},{"pid":"213dc88bf469e878d3fdd0ff2949c95bf53b347b","tid":1132897,"uid":251397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6562293546bdf23b2f55f6df01a6fe0daac14e","tid":1132897,"uid":239492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"其實好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柊老師個隻以命相搏雖然唔係為咗改變世界 佢自己都好清楚無可能 所以佢最後希望只要有人肯踏出第一步改變自己 佢已經心滿意足個下 我睇到心都酸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實所有社交平台都係同Mind Voice一樣 都係存在數唔盡唔理受害者 為講而講 隨波逐流嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dfde4fcf6fd212a378b303f96623dfce7fce16","tid":1132897,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:10:53.000Z","msg":"神作"},{"pid":"1865f8bd8d3d2f54e9cef2f2c6e7456191b6344e","tid":1132897,"uid":101399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱曬chid登仔睇"},{"pid":"c1f6877474378d0917d6c6b5d473c9bba7a048c8","tid":1132897,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"好有意義<br />\n得咁少人睇咗?"},{"pid":"9265e258cf6a37bc23eb4735f3a8adc0c16abfa4","tid":1132897,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1f6877474378d0917d6c6b5d473c9bba7a048c8","tid":1132897,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"好有意義<br />\n得咁少人睇咗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"3447abe346714e2290aa3dd26e9c8403dfbba8fa","tid":1132897,"uid":51361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20